OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy rain clears the north
OL,6,Fcoast of Aberdeenshire first thing.
OL,7,FThen sunny spells with some showers
OL,8,Fdeveloping for the afternoon. The
OL,9,Fshowers could be heavy, perhaps the
OL,10,Fodd rumble of thunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome late sunshine this
OL,13,Fevening as most showers die out. Then
OL,14,Fdry with clear spells for a time, but
OL,15,Fturning cloudier through the early
OL,16,Fhours with the odd shower possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
