OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA mainly dry, bright morning.
OL,6,FCloud will bubble up through the day
OL,7,Fto give a few afternoon showers
OL,8,Finland, while the east coast will be
OL,9,Flargely sunny.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FRain
OL,12,For showers on Tuesday and Wednesday,
OL,13,Foccasionally heavy at first. Drier on
OL,14,FThursday. Milder than of late,
OL,15,Fpotentially warm in brighter spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
